# This document tell you about how to assign ip to linux machine

1) Assin IP address to specific interface

> ifconfig eth0 192.168.10.10 netmask 255.255.255.0
> ifconfig eth0 up <---- start the interface
> ifconfig   <---- To verify that IP address is assigned successfully

2) Assign default gateway to interface

> route add default gw 192.168.10.1 eth0
> route   <---- To verify default gateway
